private static class NearestNeighborDescend.SynchronizedWeightedIndexSet
extends java.util.TreeSet<NearestNeighborDescend.WeightedIndex>
Synchronized version of a TreeSet of NearestNeighborDescend.WeightedIndex objects. It uses the weight of the weighted indices as the parameter to sort the elements by. Notice that only the following methods are synchronized:
  • add(embedding.nearestNeighbors.NearestNeighborDescend.WeightedIndex)
  • last()
  • pollLast()
